# File structure

**Goal:** Predictable, colocated, thin routes — no logic sprawl.

## Top-level map

```
app/
  (site)/          # Public RTL site — route group, no URL segment
  studio/          # Sanity Studio only
  api/             # Route handlers — contact, revalidate (see 17-security)
  globals.css      # Tailwind entry + minimal global layers
components/
  layout/          # Header, Footer, shells
  ui/              # Primitives (buttons, cards, Reveal, images)
  sections/        # Full-width homepage/marketing blocks
  content/         # CMS blocks — RichTextBody, FAQ, listings
  seo/             # JSON-LD, breadcrumbs, LCP preload
  studio/          # Studio wrapper only
lib/
  types/           # Shared DTOs — one domain per file
  cache-tags.ts    # CMS revalidation tags
  contact-schema.ts · rate-limit.ts · turnstile.ts · contact-notify.ts  # contact API
  *.ts             # Pure helpers (seo, paths, tailwind, cmsPage, navigation, …)
docs/              # Ops docs (e.g. sanity-webhook.md)
sanity/
  schemaTypes/     # One schema file per document type
  lib/             # client, queries, fetchers, image — no UI imports
scripts/           # Node maintenance (check-urdu, run-next, stubs)
deploy/            # VPS/Apache/runtime — not imported by app code
public/            # Static assets only — no CMS duplicates
```

## App Router rules

| Pattern | Rule |
|---------|------|
| Route groups | `(site)` for public pages; keep URL paths flat |
| `page.tsx` | Thin orchestrator: fetch → schema → compose sections → `notFound()` |
| `_components/` | Route-private UI — **never** imported outside that route tree |
| `[...slug]` | Catch-all for nested CMS trees (courses, services) |
| `layout.tsx` | Shared chrome only; no heavy data fetching unless layout-wide |
| `loading.tsx` / `error.tsx` | Add when route has slow CMS or user-facing failure modes |
| `revalidate` | `300` on CMS-backed public routes |

## Colocation

- New route-specific UI → `app/(site)/<route>/_components/`
- Reused twice+ across routes → promote to `components/{ui,content,sections}/`
- New Sanity type → `schemaTypes/<name>.ts` + query + fetcher + type DTO

## Import boundaries (strict)

```
app/ → components/, lib/, sanity/lib/fetchers
components/ → lib/, sanity/lib/image (not queries.ts)
lib/ → lib/ only — never components/
sanity/lib/ → lib/types — never components/ or app/
```

## Anti-patterns

- Business logic or GROQ inside `page.tsx` beyond fetch + guard
- Shared component under `app/` that other routes import
- `utils/` junk drawer — use named `lib/<domain>.ts` instead
- Duplicate static JSON when Sanity owns the content
- New top-level folders without updating `01-project.mdc` layout

## New work checklist

1. Right folder per table above
2. Data via `get*` fetchers, not inline GROQ
3. Types in `lib/types/`
4. SEO components in `components/seo/`

Skills: `new-page` · `new-leaf-route` · `new-component` · `add-fetcher`
